== Languages support ==

 * Languages: en
 * language-pack-${Languages}
 * language-pack-gnome-${Languages}

 * Languages: es de fr ru
 * language-pack-${Languages} [!powerpc]
 * language-pack-gnome-${Languages} [!powerpc]

== Ubiquity components ==

These packages make up the Ubiquity live installer.

 * ubiquity-frontend-gtk
 * ubiquity-slideshow-lubuntu [!powerpc] # Webkit broken on powerpc #996568

== Extra settings ==

 * lubuntu-live-settings

== Other ==

 * pptp-linux
 * linux-wlan-ng
 * libatm1
 * setserial
 * b43-fwcutter
 * gparted
 * feh          # Background support in ubiquity-dm mode
 * zram-config  # enable zram support with an upstart job
